Map history:


embrocation_finaled:

Changed some textures and added a variety of decals. Thanks to Patches for pointing out the weapon glitch. Spinning trap has been deleted.

dustzone version:

The spawn is changed a tad. Added smokevolume on spawnzone plus soundscapes through out the map. As last: traps, textures and tiny other things have changed. Map name is ''dustzone'' as of now.

dustzone finale:

Removed the bhop part comepletely.

I hope you'll enjoy it!
